Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{富士見大学女子バレー部合宿所}Fujimi All-girls University Volleyball Club Training Camp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{立派なお寺ね。}What a splendid mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{いないのかしら。}I wonder if they're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あっちよ。}Ah, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{え.}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん。今日は。}Good morning, Oohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{お言葉に甘えてよろしくお願いします。}Thanks for your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{よろしくお願いします。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{いらっしゃい。}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当に来ちゃっただね。}You really came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの合宿は特別厳しいのよ。}Our training camp is very strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{中学でも手加減しないから、そのつもりでね。}We won't hold back even if you're mid schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{いい？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いします。}Please look after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり来てよかったわ。}I'm glad we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん、なんだかこうしてると、修学旅行に来てるみたいね。}When we're like this, I feel like on a school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、明日からきっと扱かれるわよ。}Well, I'm sure it'll get tough tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{望む所よ。}Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、起きて起きて。}Come on, wake up, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体何時まで寝ってんの？}How long do you want to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、未だ六時ですよ。}Oh, it's still six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{何言ってるの。}What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆もう朝のトレーニングに入ってるのよ。}We're readying for the morning training already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなに早く？}This early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{朝には弱いんだ、あたし。}I feel weak in mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、しっかりして。}Pull it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ぐずぐずしてと置いて行くよ。}We'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:34.87,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{すごい。}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.26,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり大学のハードトレーニングは違うわ。}The university training's truly something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{そこの二人前出て。}You two, step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{—はい。\N—はい。}– Yes.\N– Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{—今日からあたしたちと一緒にやろうね。良い？\N—はい。}– We'll practice together from today. Got it?\N– Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{びしびし行ったらそのつもりです。}I won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちびたち、頑張って。}Do your best, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうそうそうそう。}Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{—それ！\N—えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って！}Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり、しっかり。}Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{フエン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり。}Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、どうした。}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールに追ってくる。}Bring the ball back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXしない。}Don't space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、立って。}Come on, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり、しっかり。}Keep at it, keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ未だ。}There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{プレー！}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ未だ。}More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{アン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}I won't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり、まこ。}Get a grip, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{アフン。}Ahn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、頑張ってよ。}Come on, win already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、強いわ。}Ah, she's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ちびちゃんもしっかり。}The little one's has it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けそうよ。}I'm losing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ほら。}Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、負けた。}Ahh, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごい、鮎原さん。四人も言ったわよ。}Amazing, Ayuhara-san. It's your fourth victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、今度あたしは相手よ。}All right, I'll be your opponent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん。}Oohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、困ったな。もうダメです。}Ah, I don't think I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{—左手ならお相手し…\N—え？あなた、左手が強いの？}– But if we go with left hands—\N– Huh, so you have a strong left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。左の方が自身あるんです。}Yep. I'm pretty confident about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、左でいきましょう。}Well then, let's try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って。}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{雪辱よ。}Save our honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{これは面白いわ。}This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って。}Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン、しっかり。}Captain, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{良い?いくわよ。}Ready? Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうぞ。}Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ちびちゃんもしっかり。}Good luck, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン、しっかり。}Captain, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{まいった。大原さん、すごいわ。}Ah, I lost. Oohara-san, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたこそ。}Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなに左は強いなら、あなたは最優両手のアタッカーに成れるわよ。}With a left hand this strong, you can become an excellent ambidextrous attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.06,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{最優両手のアタッカー。}Ambidextrous attacker…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごいXXXのアタックね。}Amazing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり思った通りだわ。}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれがずばずば決まるよう成ったら、あたしたちでも受けきれるかどうか分からないわよ。}Once she perfects it, I'm not sure if we'd be able to protect against it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXかったわ。}Who would've think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{両刀使いのアタッカー何て…ちょっといないんじゃない？}Aren't attackers that can use both hands very rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あれだけじゃ…}But that's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ未だ泉さん達、四天王に勝てる自身はないわ。}I still don't think we can win with Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうね。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{問題はあの変化球サーブを…どうやって受けるかね。}The problem is how to receive that curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{後五日しかないのに。}We have five more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしよう？}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりそうだったの。}So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん。}Oohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの合宿に参加したのは、なんか理由があると思っただけど…}I figured there had to be a reason as to why you wanted to participate in our camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{い、いいえ、あの…あの、その…}Ah, that's not it… err…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちそれだけで来たじゃないです。}That's not all what we came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。つまり、その…専心しようのために。}She's right. We also wanted to improve our focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理しなくてもいいのよ。}Don't push yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝つために練習することは恥ずかしいことじゃないだから。}There's nothing shameful in training to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{その四天王XX人達の噂あたしたちもう聞いてるけど、そんなにすごいの？}We've heard somewhat about that "Big Four" ourselves. Are they really this amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{コートのキャプテンの泉さんのサーブはものすごいです。}Captain Izumi-san's serve is particularly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{サーブが？}Her serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{目の前でストーンと落ちる。}It falls before eyes like a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ものすごい変化球なんです。}It's a really remarkable curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{目の前で落ちる…}Falls before the eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと、いらっしゃい。}Come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ…}Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしのサーブを受けてごらんなさい。}Try to receive my serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{jーはい。\N—はい。}– Yes ma'am.\N– Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくわよ。}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{お…}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{これです。}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{この変化球です。}That's her curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりそう。}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{このサーブはね…}This serve…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは「木の葉おとし」と呼んでるの。}We call it "falling leaf".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{「木の葉おとし」…}"Falling leaf"…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、この変化球が使える何て、その泉さんはて言う人は…大した人よ。}But Izumi-san is a remarkable person if she can use this curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、ちびちゃんたち、心配しなくてもいいわ。}But don't you worry, sweeties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちなら、練習次第で、十分この変化球が使えるようになるから。}With your skill and a little practice, you'll learn how to serve it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみる？}Wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちこのサーブの打ち方より、受け方の方が覚えたいんです。}But rather than learning how to serve it, we'd prefer to learn how to receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{受け方を教えてください。}Please tell us how to receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{—お願いします。\N—お願いします。}– Please.\N– Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{お断りよ。}I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{もういいから、さっさと荷物まとめておかえりなさい。}All right, hurry up and collect your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん、待ってください。}Oohara-san, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いします。}We're begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの変化球の受け方をどうぞ教えてください。}Please teach us how to receive that curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんなに辛くても、頑張ります。教えてください。}No matter the difficulty, we'll endure. Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{いやよ。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしてですか。}Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち、何か間違えいてるんじゃないの？}Aren't you two missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{攻撃は最大の防御て言う言葉を知らないの？}Don't you know the proverb, "the attack is the best defense"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくらレシーブはできたって、試合には勝てないのよ。}No matter how good you are at\hreceiving, it won't win you a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーではね…}In volleyball…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{相手の最も得意な技を逆に力XX的に勝つ方法なのよ。}The best way to win is to use your opponent's techniques against themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんな人だって、自分の得意技を相手に使われるぐらいショックなXXないわよ。}Everyone is shocked when they see their enemy able to use their techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かる？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{コートにサーブはね…}In the court, the serve…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーで一番大切な武器だってこと忘れちゃダメよ。}…is the prime weapon. Don't you forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:09.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{さすがは、何度も優勝したことあるキャプテンは違うわ。}As expected, an experienced captain is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かったら、サーブの練習。良いわね。}Now that you get it, it's serving practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ。}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの…}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{何?}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言う風に打てばいいでしょう？}What kind of strike should I go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは自分で研究するの。}You should discover it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちはとてもあんな変化球は…}But… for us, that kind of curve ball…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{なに言ってるの。}What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{打ち方さえ教わればできるとでも思ってるの？}Think you'll learn it just by having it described to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{それだったら、(XXX・題)だってできるじゃないの？}Then same goes to school exams, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当にXXXしたかったらね。}You really need to put in an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{もっと基本から(XXX・苦労)するの。}Focus on the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{一言だけヒントを上げるわ。}I'll give you one hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{この変化球の秘訣わね…}The secret behind this curve ball…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{手の当て方にやるの。}…is in the way the hand hits the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{手の当て方？}The way the hand hits the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体どう言う風に？}What is the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。やってごらんなさい。}All right! Let's see you try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメね。}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{全然変化しないじゃい。}It doesn't sway one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{手首よ。手首。}The wrist. Use your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。早川さんにかわって。}All right, switch with Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目駄目、二人共。}That's no good, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことでは泉さんに勝てないわよ。}You won't win with Izumi-san this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{もっと真剣にやりなさい。}Do it more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、今からサーブの練習百球。}Well then, try 100 serves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわね。}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{—はい。\N—はい。}– Yes.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:33.78,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:36.85,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{これをできなければ、絶対に四天王に勝てないんだわ。}If we can't do this, there's no\hway we'll win with the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…あん。}Ah… ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？悔しかったら、あたしに勝つことね。}How is it? If you're frustrated, win with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:17.80,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{やる。}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.61,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{絶対にやるわ。}I'll win with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、起きるのよ。}Raise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{あん。}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目だ。}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしてもできない。}No matter how I try…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.13,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{回転しないボールが沈んだ。}The ball didn't rotate and it sank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:55.74,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{今まで落とす、落とすXXX玉に回転は与えるにXXXしてだけど…}Until now, I thought the proper rotation was crucial for it to fall early…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.83,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{玉に回転は与えずに打つ。}…but I haven't tried giving it no rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かった。これだわ。}That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。もう一度お願い。}Midori-san, let's try once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{受けてくれる？}Can you receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわ。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわ、鮎原さん。}You did it, Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう一息よ。}Let's try it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね。}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫？}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫よ。}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、ちょっと休みましょう。}Midori-san, let's rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目。今止めちゃう、折角XXXだ。}No. You're getting the hang of\hit. You can't lose your focus now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、続けて。}Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう、みどりさん。}Thank you, Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん…}Midori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわ。}You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたやったのよ。}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわ。}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{到頭。}Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{—やったわ。\N—やった！やった。}– Hooray!\N– We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。(XXX・でっちゃう)わ。XXX…}– Ah… I'm crying…\N– Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん…あなたは…素晴らしい人だわ。}Ayuhara-san, you truly are an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、あなたも直ぐやれるわ。}Midori-san, you'll figure it out soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.37,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{二人共、良くやったわ。}You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.83,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{あとは力よ。}What's left is the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.27,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{スピードはXXX、「木の葉おとし」XXXだから。}The key to make the falling leaf the most effective is the proper speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.16,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{そうなると、もう完璧よ。}With that, it'll be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.88,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{本当によくやった。}You really did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{偉いわ。}Good girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.91,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1850,0)}{富士見学園}Fujimi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{おお？}Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、本郷先生、あなたどうしてもバレー部のコーチに成ると仰るですか。}Then professor Hongou, are you saying you want to be the volleyball club's coach no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{今のバレー部は…}As of now, the club…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸で犬と猿な集まり見たいで、全然纏まりありません。}…is like cats and dogs.\NThey don't work together at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{それぐらい私にも分かっています。}I noticed that much myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ何ですか？}What is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは私の責任だと言いたいんですか。}Are you saying it is my responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{いえ、梶岡先生。}No, professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただ、あなたは富士見学園と浜紀中と今だ差別してXます。}I think you're biased in your treatment of Fujimi's and Hamaki's students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{—それじゃ、いつまで立っても…\N—ちょっと、待ってください。}– No matter what—\N– Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ誤解ですよ、本郷先生。}It's a misunderstanding, professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{私は何もXXXそんな…}For me to be biased…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{誤解？いいえ。それならそれで結構です。}Misunderstanding? If that is the case, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、とにかく今のバレー部はバラバラです。}But at any rate, the club's in pieces right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれを一つに纏めないかぎり、春の全日本選手権大会に出ても。}Until they've reunited, even if we make it to the spring All-Japan Tournament…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{…とても勝てる見込みはありません。}…there is really no hope for winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、あなたはコーチに成れば、優勝出きると言うんですな？}So if you become a coach, you'll lead them to a victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。やってみます。}Yes. I want to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{もしできなかったら？}What if you fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん、その時に責任をとります。}Of course, I'll take responsibility for that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{責任？}Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。梶岡先生。}Ah, professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここは一つ…}Why don't we…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{若い本郷先生にお任せしてみようじゃありませんか？}…leave it to the young and ambitious professor Hongou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{結構です。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこまでやれるか、ゆっくり拝見ざしていただきましょう。}Let's see how far he can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、失礼。}Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫かな、本郷先生？}Will it be all right, professor Hongou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だか、あの梶岡先生は浜紀中の四天王を育て上げた、実力者だからね。}After all, professor Kajioka, having raised the\hfamed Hamaki's Big Four, is a powerful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん。その転送浮けしています。}Of course, I understand that part very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、一番大事のはチームワークです。}But the teamwork is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原や早川があの四天王と手を組めば、優勝は先ず絶対です。}If Ayuhara and Hayakawa make up with the Big Four, they'll be invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。問題はそれだが。}Hmm… the problem is how they get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.62,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{そうだ。}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.19,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{まさに問題がそれだ。}That is exactly the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:50.85,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.09,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{早川。}Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.18,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{僕の君達にかける期待は大きいのだ。}I have big hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.48,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{あと3日で学校は始まる。}The school starts in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.99,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{あとは君達の出番だ。}After that, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{頼むぞ。}I'm counting on you.
