Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さん、有難うございました。}Oohara-san, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXすれば、(XXX・跳ね上げる・羽を上げる)だろうと思ったのに。}I thought you'd drop out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{とうとう最後まで頑張りとしたのね。}You both worked hard until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのファイトはあるかぎりも、誰にも負けないわ。}If you keep up this attitude, you won't lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張るのよ。}Work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{でももっと時間あれば、色々と教えていただきたいことがたくさんあったんです。}But had we more time, I'd have a chance to learn much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{残念です。}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん、大丈夫よ。}Nah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{技術的に教えることは何もないわ。}There's nothing practical I can teach you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、体に気をつけてね。}Well then, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆さんも、どうぞお元気で。}You too. Please stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{有難う御座いました。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{バイバイ！頑張ってね！}Bye-bye! Till next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.20,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{見ててください。}Just look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.70,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{このXXXは明日から始まる学校のコートでしますから。}Tomorrow the school starts. We'll shine in the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{鮎原}Ayuhara family
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただいま。}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえちゃん。}Kozue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパ、ママ。}Papa! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、おかえり。}Hey. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{おかえりなさい。}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{驚くじゃないぞ、こずえ。}Don't be surprised, Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパやママは、今日からお前と一緒にこの富士見や浜暮らすことになったんだよ。}From today on, me and your mom will live with you in Fujimihama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ、本当？}Wah, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当よ。}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパはね、今度こっちの支社転勤に成ったの。}Papa's company transferred him here this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ、うれしい。これからずっと一緒にいられるのね。}Wah, I'm so happy! We'll be together forever from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり本物のパパやママには勝てないな。}Looks like we can't win to the actual dad and mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:41.95,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1810,500)}{富士見学園}Fujimi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{３年４組}Year 3 class 4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{これで、学級委員は、一ノ瀬努くんと鮎原こずえさんに決まりました。}With that, the class representatives will be Ichinose Tsutomu-kun and Ayuhara Kozue-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{おめでとう。}Nice! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{おめでとう、鮎原さん。}Congratulations, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{冗談じゃないわ、私なんか学級委員てからじゃないわよ。}Give me a break. I'm not fit for this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、そう言うなよ。}Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{折角僕達は選んだ代表なんだからさ。}We've all earnestly elected you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{それよ。ほらほら。}– That's right.\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、大変よ、親分。}Troubles again, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの、柏木さん？}What's wrong, Kashiwagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{大変なのよ。四天王は…}It's the Big Four…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王は？}What about the Big Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{体育館のコート独占し、あたしたちに使えないのよ。どうする、親分。}They've completely occupied the gym.\NWe can't use it anymore. What do we do, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、行こう。}– Midori-san, let's go.\N– Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい、待ちたまえ。}Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生。}Professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達。正式に私が、バレー部のコーチに決まった。}It's official. I've been chosen as the club's coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{—今まで通りやるぞ。\N—え？}– We'll continue as before.\N– Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、一つだけ言っておきたい。}But I want to make one thing clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕は何も、浜紀中の連中をボイコットするためにバレー部のコーチに成ったんじゃないからな。}I didn't became the coach to\hexclude the Hamaki's bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かりました。}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうか。それじゃいいよ。}I see. Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{新しいバレー部には、新しいチームワークは必要なんだ。}The new club needs new teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのために、君達はあの四天王手を握ってXX欲しいんだ。}To realize it, I want you to make\hup and unite with the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{よく分かりました、先生。}I understand that well, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:22:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、仲良くなれためには、その前にXXならないことがあります。}But to call a truce, there's something we must do first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:05.27,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{XXXならないこと？うん。}Something you must do? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ぼやぼやしないで玉拾いXXしたらどう？}Don't just sit there.\NWhy don't you fetch us that ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼ね。}How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXでしょう？}You can do that yourself, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんですって。}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたら球拾いは補欠の仕事だって知らないの？}Don't you know that fetching balls is a substitutes' work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは補欠？}We're substitutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなこと誰が決めたのよ。}Who decided that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{梶岡先生よ。}Professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見しっしの選手は全員補欠ですって。}He declared all members from Fujimi to be our substitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{お分かり？}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{コーチの命令は絶対でしょう？}The coach's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう思うでしょう?}Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{お生憎様、バレー部のコーチは今日から本郷先生よ。}Sorry to disappoint you, but our coach is now professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{—え？そんなバカな。\N—梶岡先生は？}– Eh? That's ridiculous.\N– What about professor Kajioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{陸上部のコーチですって。}He's said to be track and field club's coach now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、皆さんも陸上部にをXXXなったら？}How about you all join track and field club too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{—ははは。\N—泉さん。}– Hahaha.\N– Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{心配しなくても良いわよ。}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{誰がコーチになろうと、実力がすべてを決めるのよ。}No matter the coach, what really matters is the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、そ、そ、そう言うこと。}Ah, th-th-that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{大きなXXだって、やっぱりあんたたちは全員補欠てことよ。}In the end you're all worth to be just substitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXないでね。}Don't get ahead of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{レギュラーに成りたきゃ、先ずあたしたちに勝つことね。}To become regulars, you need to defeat us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、それはXX不可能ね。}But it's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんのサーブ一つ受けられないあなたたちには。}You can't receive a single Izumi-san's serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、そうかしら？}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。}Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよあたしたちの出番が来たようね。}Finally, it is our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{出番？それどう言う意味？}Your turn? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{この前の返しをさせてもらうてことよ。}We want to repay for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち。あたしたちに勝てるつもりなの？}Do you really think you can win with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみなきゃ分かんない、それは。}We won't know unless we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{やる気なの？}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:36.11,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ大学バレー部の合宿で鍛えた成果を試す時が来たわ。}It's time to test the results of the training at university volleyball camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.83,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{木の葉おとす。}Falling leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.75,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{木の葉おとしのXXX試す時が。}It's time to see what impact a falling leaf can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:59.29,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{浜紀学園との合併XX、ますます対立するアタックコンビと四天王…}Since the Hamaki merge, there's been a conflict between the attack duo and the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:04.37,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{だが、本郷先生はコーチに決まったことから、ますます対立は激しくなる。}But now that professor Hongou is the\hcoach, the conflict only deepens further.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:10.11,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{得に、四天王の一人泉の反発は、部員達が驚くほどの激し浚った。}Izumi puts up a particular opposition, surprising the other club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:12.80,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{本郷コーチは実力第一と言う…}Professor Hongou acknowledges that skill is crucial…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:17.90,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{…そこで試合におって、どちらが実力なあるか、決着を決めることになった。}…and thus the girls hold a match to prove whose skill is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:22.13,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
